schools.name: Bonita Springs Middle Center For The Arts

data.description: Beautiful hidden tropical paradise just minutes from the historic Bonita Springs River Park.  3/2 waterfront home on canal where the dolphins and manatee swim.  Large back yard with boat dock just a 10 minute kayak paddle to the river park area or a 25 minute motor ride to the gulf beaches and back bay areas. This home had NO flood damage from Ian!   3/2 layout with many upgrades to make it a move in ready home.  Appliances are all in excellent condition, replaced within 5 years.  Roof is 4 years old (no hurricane damage), whole house has been replumbed approximately 6 months ago, cabinets refaced, new flooring, large work shed, back yard pergola, spa, new privacy fence, large koi pond, privacy landscaping in the front yard, new master bath, screened in lanai and much more.  Live the Florida lifestyle with a morning sunrise from your screened in lanai or bbq on the outdoor patio area in the late afternoon overlooking the water. Located minutes from fine dining, shopping in Bonita Springs and just a 10 minute drive to the beaches.  Make this your home or a great vacation rental property.
